{"tid":1365883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥唔係一個人，係一個現象。","createTime":"2019-07-25T19:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:27:42.000Z","uid":48259,"like":77,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f57906770c0ad47de87f236d849df72b89a5f1","tid":1365883,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:24:51.000Z","msg":"首先，唔該大家唔好覺得達狗呢排出黎講幾句野就什麼達哥歸隊了。佢既行為我眼中仍然係十分虛偽，甚至越來越討厭。<br />\n<br />\n大家唔係唔知最近示威者民意急線上升，香港大部人都發左聲支持，所以好多從前深潛既人會慢慢出番黎，但我想大家要記住呢班人，因為佢地從來都唔係手足，只係牆頭草，睇利益做人。<br />\n<br />\n達哥，一切已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係歸隊，唔該你宣傳下7&middot;27，兼且身體力行入元朗。行動永遠勝過千言萬語，你肯咁做果話，我支持番你又點話？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1033c60136cdace14cfc5df38ec19e77f56d6f24","tid":1365883,"uid":48259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"推到比達哥睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22effaae1281abad6118dcfa99851235bcd06e0","tid":1365883,"uid":48259,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:28:43.000Z","msg":"達哥原來仲有咁多支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7a275f7101cd1b902cef1d0d3e9620d43ea68e","tid":1365883,"uid":174289,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:29:50.000Z","msg":"做咩都無用，巳經心淡<br />\n<br />\n金錢奴隸達"},{"pid":"96687698876e03094a4c7cb9f57744f8dc6682ea","tid":1365883,"uid":123264,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:30:06.000Z","msg":"依家出黎既人可以幸免於難<br />\n唔會逼害達哥<br />\n但想我番去佢chat room嘿嘿哈哈 不了"},{"pid":"b0d4c8870a7fd28c1995475f19f19b81fe43d504","tid":1365883,"uid":38482,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:30:34.000Z","msg":"算啦佢只會揀啲唔會得失兩面既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nexample:叫人唔好自殺<br />\n佢邊敢會講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達哥已經變了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbf7b61cae211e4bdf7f23140c80cee435517f6","tid":1365883,"uid":123264,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:31:03.000Z","msg":"你男朋友係你比人強姦果陣唔出聲 由你比人強姦<br />\n事後先出聲 你點睇佢?"},{"pid":"71f9c34993f58f4ebfbeaf291c6b74a4425af181","tid":1365883,"uid":10422,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"佢呢招都唔係第一次啦，嗰期講緊佔中，扮支持港人&gt;得到大多數後生支持&gt;出撚左名&gt;搵大錢，癡中資&gt;香港患難，扮中立，食兩家茶禮&gt;兄弟覺醒被佢屌引戰狗&gt;紅媒知佢無利用價值補刀&gt;迖哥又扮支持立場新聞&gt;無事又開台玩支那gAme搵香港人錢&gt;下次香港出事&gt;loop到2047"},{"pid":"3db3ced535be4e1e9948bfba81913a8942738fcd","tid":1365883,"uid":48259,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0fbf7b61cae211e4bdf7f23140c80cee435517f6","tid":1365883,"uid":123264,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:31:03.000Z","msg":"你男朋友係你比人強姦果陣唔出聲 由你比人強姦<br />\n事後先出聲 你點睇佢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:33:49.000Z","msg":"一切已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔想見到有班兄弟比佢呃"},{"pid":"48546e31da2d31e83ee018994cf20510c5be842b","tid":1365883,"uid":167878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:34:16.000Z","msg":"达哥係咪收咗錢出嚟搞分化<br />\n用佢班護主犬分化香港人"},{"pid":"013404b5df68569b702c786efb2f24bcf97591f6","tid":1365883,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"48546e31da2d31e83ee018994cf20510c5be842b","tid":1365883,"uid":167878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:34:16.000Z","msg":"达哥係咪收咗錢出嚟搞分化<br />\n用佢班護主犬分化香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:37:20.000Z","msg":"唔係咁玩法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c116626b2824b173f8b300a3d6d937880b048e56","tid":1365883,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:39:09.000Z","msg":"post